Brisbane River. The queen, who has been touring Australia's outback
for three weeks, is on her llth visit to Australia.
   The $460 million Expo '88, with its theme of ``Leisure In The
Age Of Technology,'' has attracted exhibits from 36 countries. It
will be open until Oct. 30 and is expected to attract 7.8 million
visitors.
   The last World Expo staged in Australia was 100 years ago.
